Try to write the requirements for simple arcade style driving game where the player has to 
navigate around obstacles to keep from crashing.

Requirements:
1. Have a model for the car exterior/interior depending if 1st or 3rd person (Mandatory)
2. Obstacles of different kinds (Optional)
3. Crashing animation (Madatory)
4. Road type/Way to switch lanes and avoid obstacles (Mandatory)
5. Menu for user to start, exit, and play again when they lose (Optional)
6. Animations get faster for harder difficulty over time, or a difficulty switching option (Optional)
7. Timer for scoring depending how long the user lasts (Optional)
